<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Payment Successful - MIRA Dashboard</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.0/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
    <style>
        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
        }
        .success-container {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 3rem;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
            max-width: 500px;
        }
        .success-icon {
            font-size: 5rem;
            color: #00ff88;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        .btn-dashboard {
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #00ff88, #00cc66);
            border: none;
            padding: 0.75rem 2rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            border-radius: 25px;
            color: white;
            transition: transform 0.2s;
            margin-top: 1rem;
        }
        .btn-dashboard:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            color: white;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="success-container">
        <i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill success-icon"></i>
        <h1>Payment Successful!</h1>
        <p class="lead">Your tokens have been added to your account.</p>
        <p>Thank you for your purchase. You can now use your tokens to perform actions in Discord servers.</p>
        <a href="/dashboard" class="btn btn-dashboard">
            <i class="bi bi-arrow-left"></i> Return to Dashboard
        </a>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 